**View Web Hosting Account Information**

Now customers can view their account plan details from client portal. To view that go to **Menu** >> **Billing** >> Click on the **plan name** under **Hosting plan**. 

```diagram

```

**PrePay**

Now customers can make prepayment on their account. To do that go to **Menu** >> **Billing** >> Click on the **plan name** under **Hosting plan** >> Click on **Pre-pay**. 

Then **Choose a payment term** from the drop down list. 

```diagram

```

**Billing Cycle**

Web hosting customers can change their billing cycle from one month to 3, 6 , 12 and up to 48 months.  To do that go to **Menu** >> **Billing** >> Click on the **plan name** under **Hosting plan** >> Click on **Billing Cycle**.

Then choose a **Billing Cycle** from the drop down list. This will take effect on the next billing date.

